room_title: Escape room "Spies Vs. Spies" by Trapped Puzzle Rooms in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: There was a group of 12 of us with kids ranging in ages from 10-21. We did the Spies Vs. Spies room and has so much fun! We will absolutely do this again! Eric was a great game leader too!

room_title: Escape room "Spies Vs. Spies" by Trapped Puzzle Rooms in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: My family and I had a great time at the Spies vs. Spies rooms. It was a lot of fun, very engaging for everybody. I would absolutely encourage people to go check this out, it was a blast. We can't wait to do the next room.

room_title: Escape room "Spies Vs. Spies" by Trapped Puzzle Rooms in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: Had a great time in Spies vs Spies room at the St. Paul location. Highly recommend this place.

room_title: Escape room "Spies Vs. Spies" by Trapped Puzzle Rooms in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: We had an awesome time in the room! Spies vs. Spies really made it a competition and the clues were just hard enough to make you think! The staff was awesome and friendly!I'll definitely be looking to come here again and try another room!

room_title: Escape room "Spies Vs. Spies" by Trapped Puzzle Rooms in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: We did the Spies vs Spies and had a blast! Really gets you thinking and working as a team. The employees we very nice and welcoming. You can tell that they like what they do!
